title.narrative: Strengthening the competitiveness, organizational performance and export capacity of the Cuban music industry

description.narrative: The main goal of the project is to strengthen the creative industry as a mechanism for employment generation and economic diversification in Cuba. More specifically the objective is to implement a pilot demonstrative case for increasing the industry#s competitiveness, promote entrepreneurship and extends the export value of the Cuban music industry. This will be achieved by improving articulation and synergies along all the stages of the Cuban music business value chain, by upgrading production technologies, promoting partnerships and strategic alliances as well as developing international marketing and distribution strategies
